  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        advanced Parkinson's disease with UPDRS III score &gt;29/104 or Dyskinesia score &gt; 2 or tremor
        &gt;2

        Exclusion Criteria:

        age&gt;75 years depression psychosis surgical contraindications
      </textblock>
